name: material mapping
desc: This module can re-assign data for the purpose of grouping.这个模块可以重新分配数据进行分组。

properties.name: Value Type
properties.desc: The Value Type radio selector determines the type of data to be modified.值类型选择器确定要修改的数据类型。

properties.name: Activate Mapping
properties.desc: The Activate Mapping toggle turns on or off the current material mapping.此开关打开或关闭当前材质映射。

properties.name: From Value
properties.desc: The From Value specifies the starting range to map from.指定要映射的起始范围。

properties.name: To Value
properties.desc: The To Value specifies the ending range to map from.指定要映射的结束范围

properties.name: Map Value
properties.desc: The Map Value specifies the desired value to map everything from the From Value to the To Value to.指定所需的新值来映射从起始值到结束值的所有内容。

properties.name: Map Name
properties.desc: The Name for the Mapped Material.  This is used when creating the Geology Legend port.映射材料的名称。这在创建地质图例端口时使用。
